{
  "texts": [
    "To apply the test, the predictions of the models are needed at the sentence level.",
    "Therefore, we asked the authors of the respective publications to provide the source code in order to generate the predictions.",
    "We have received the code for the previous state-of-the-art models for NIC (PSOTA-NIC) and ART (PSOTA-ART) datasets.",
    "In our tests, MULT ALL and MULT GRP models are compared with each other, with PSOTA-NIC and PSOTA-ART, and with the different SciBERT-HSLN models.",
    "Additionally, the significance between SciBERT-HSLN models and the existing PSOTAs has been checked."
  ]
}